 is the more chaste, (TA,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A camel, male or female;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, Msb, K;) as applied to a camel, like"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_inosaAnN", "text_ar": "اـِنْسَانٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "applied to a human being; (S, Msb;) whereas"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jamalN", "text_ar": "جَمَلٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is applied only to a male camel, and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "naAqapN", "text_ar": "نَاقَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "to a she-camel;"}, {"kind": "page_break", "n": 227}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "bakorN", "text_ar": "بَكْرٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "bakorapN", "text_ar": "بَكْرَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "are respectively terms like"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "fatnFY", "text_ar": "فَتنًى"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "fataApN", "text_ar": "فَتَاةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qaluwSN", "text_ar": "قَلُوصٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is like the term"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jaAriyapN", "text_ar": "جَارِيَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; so say, among others, ISk and Az and IJ; and it is added in the Mutahffidh, that the terms"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jml", "text_ar": "جمل"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "nAqp", "text_ar": "ناقة"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "are applied only when the animal has entered the seventh year: (Msb:) but"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "bEyr", "text_ar": "بعير"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is more commonly applied to the"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "male camel;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb, K;) and only to"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "one that has entered its fifth year;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, K;) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "that has entered its ninth year:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K:) the pl. is"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_b